snippet.title: The Mask: Mayhem in Hard mode & No Rolldodge 73x Full Combo | Hotline Miami 2 (level editor)
snippet.description:
Lagging..................... That's why i had to find some strats where roll dodge is not necessary. Unique playstyle i think))) 

Лаги................. Из-за них я старался не использовать кувырки. Уникальность, я думаю))) 

Music used:
Kinky - Uruapan Breaks as level theme
Aphex Twin - Stone in Focus as Videodrome
Home - 14 as Score summary.

300 subs special? Hunter snowfall 2016 i think
